Classes in de.frankfurt.uni.vcp.net used by de.frankfurt.uni.vcp
ProtocolError
           This class is used for networking Exception handling An Exception of type ProtocolError will be thrown, whenever the client receives a package, that doesn't seem to conform to the game protocol specification.
